ERRORS/MISCELLANEOUS
--------------------
The Irix 6 hints file was hacked to ignore 64bit mode which it seems to
want to default to when os is IRIX64.
Also because we're building with gcc 3.4.x the -DIRIX32_SEMUN_BROKEN_BY_GCC
define was removed since that ABI problem was fixed in this version.
